ENTRY       EC 3.4.24.30                Enzyme
NAME        coccolysin;
            Streptococcus thermophilus intracellular proteinase;
            EM 19000
CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Acting on peptide bonds (peptidases);
            Metalloendopeptidases
REACTION    Preferential cleavage: !Leu, !Phe, !Tyr, !Ala
COMMENT     A 30 kDa endopeptidase found intracellularly in S. thermophilus [1] and S. diacetilactis [2] and in the medium of S. faecalis [3,4]. In peptidase family M4 (thermolysin family). Formerly included in EC 3.4.24.4
